== 1.0.5

* Hacks to allow for new Hashie versions. See https://github.com/intridea/hashie/issues/14

== 1.0.4

* Better error handling
* Ignoring Gemfile.lock
* Removing call to #blank? as that requires Rails
* Returning an empty array when Metric#to_array handles a response w/no records rather than raising an exception

== 1.0.3

* Fixing response header change w/HTTParty 0.8
* Removed broken rake console rake task

== 1.0.2

* Removed Server#active_alerts. This XML is not being returned.
* Changed require calls to relative paths
* No longer requiring a specific version of HTTParty to fix compatibly issues w/Ruby Gems 1.6+

== 1.0.1

* Removed debugging output in Metric#to_sparkline

== 1.0.0

* Updates for YARD documentation formatting

== 0.9.1

* Fixed Ruby 1.9.2 issue accessing Server#key
* Documentation updates

== 0.9.0

Initial release.